2026-05-16T20:37:38.5621675Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T20:37:38.5622390Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T20:37:38.5623084Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T20:37:38.5623880Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T20:37:38.5624632Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T20:37:38.5625380Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
