2026-05-16T20:37:38.8123156Z 21    <!--
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8123502Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8123680Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8124005Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8124298Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8124602Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8125124Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8125441Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8125744Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8126045Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8126581Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8126730Z 32    -->
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8127098Z 33    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
