2026-05-16T20:37:38.8369168Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8369486Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T20:37:38.8369786Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
